<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Aug1938"><font color="red">22 August 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  Thank you for your letter of August 19th. I have written to our printers telling them to hold up the paging when they have got to the end of Section 2, part II; so I await Mr Joyce&apos;s further instructions. </div>
